1
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:17,900
Everyone who has used this drug

2
00:00:20,690 --> 00:00:22,830
will eventually be killed by me.

3
00:00:29,110 --> 00:00:29,880
Mentor,

4
00:00:34,290 --> 00:00:35,640
will you kill me, too?

5
00:00:55,860 --> 00:00:57,410
Actually, I can do it myself

6
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:00,450
instead of bothering you.

7
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:04,400
You don't know what you'll become.

8
00:01:06,110 --> 00:01:07,310
When that time comes,

9
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:10,620
only I can do it.

10
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:12,680
What about you?

11
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:15,840
It's not fair to you.

12
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:20,270
At a time like this,

13
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:22,030
can you stop worrying about me?

14
00:01:23,730 --> 00:01:25,210
We owe you our lives.

15
00:01:25,770 --> 00:01:29,360
-If we hadn't met you back then...
-Then why didn’t you listen to me?

16
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:31,490
Why did you insist on going to Nanyang?

17
00:01:32,590 --> 00:01:34,920
Isn't this the ending you chose yourself?

18
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,180
If killing me

19
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,370
will bring you pain,

20
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:03,110
I'd rather die on the way
to kill Mo Yungao.

21
00:02:18,970 --> 00:02:19,800
Next,

22
00:02:21,810 --> 00:02:24,070
please leave the hardest missions to me.

23
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:32,290
Just consider it

24
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,490
me being willful one last time.

25
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:57,920
Okay.

26
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:00,960
Suit yourself.

27
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,630
I was paralyzed in Nanyang for 3 years,

28
00:03:11,370 --> 00:03:13,170
and he took care of me for 3 years.

29
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:16,090
This is not what I wanted.

30
00:03:17,930 --> 00:03:20,260
It's the last outcome
I ever wished to see.

31
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,540
Do whatever you like.

32
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:42,780
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

33
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:45,830
[Episode 18]

34
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:57,780
[Here rests my late father,
Mr. Dong Shi Chang]

35
00:05:57,870 --> 00:06:03,850
[Erected faithfully by the daughter,
Dong Zhuohua]

36
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:06,180
[Xiacheng Law Firm]
[Last Will and Testament]

37
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:09,360
[Testator: Dong Shichang]
[Recipient: Zhang Haiqi]

38
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,680
My Lady,

39
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:22,950
are you really going to dismiss everyone
in the Dong family

40
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:25,210
and leave Xiacheng to live abroad alone?

41
00:06:26,330 --> 00:06:28,670
Please let us stay and take care of you.

42
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,350
Don't bother.

43
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:34,350
About the Dong family's property,

44
00:06:34,860 --> 00:06:37,010
I will transfer it to Father's nephew.

45
00:06:37,450 --> 00:06:41,830
[Here rests my late father,
Mr. Dong Shi Chang]

46
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:45,950
Let me have some time alone

47
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,180
with my father.

48
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,890
I specifically chose this cemetery.

49
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,540
So you and your real daughter

50
00:07:14,010 --> 00:07:14,750
can reunite.

51
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,860
Zhuohua.

52
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,450
Zhuohua!

53
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,100
Thank you

54
00:08:01,530 --> 00:08:03,790
for lending me your identity for so long.

55
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:07,260
I'm returning Miss Dong's identity to you.

56
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,150
Please rest in peace.

57
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:25,000
Life is but a fleeting encounter.

58
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,130
Nothing

59
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:30,000
lasts forever.

60
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:12,650
[Xiacheng to Changxiang]

61
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,860
You know what?

62
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:15,910
My mother is

63
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:18,630
very easygoing.

64
00:09:18,630 --> 00:09:19,790
She likes whatever I like.

65
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:21,990
Sir, would you like to buy some flowers?

66
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,040
I'll take one.

67
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:24,960
Here.

68
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,590
Here you are.

69
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,720
Thank you.

70
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:29,640
No problem.

71
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,120
Would you like to buy some flowers?

72
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:31,860
No, thanks.

73
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:32,870
Okay.

74
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:37,010
Sir, would you like to buy some flowers
for the lady?

75
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:38,630
No, thanks. I'm his mother.

76
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:42,180
My mother had me when she was young.

77
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:44,340
I'll take the whole basket.

78
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:46,040
Thank you, sir.

79
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:47,320
Thank you, lady.

80
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,250
What are you looking at?

81
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,130
Mentor,

82
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:07,440
didn't you say

83
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,970
we should keep a low profile
during this trip?

84
00:10:10,370 --> 00:10:11,840
Why does it feel like
every man in this carriage

85
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,300
wants to be my stepfather?

86
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:15,460
I was born beautiful.

87
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:17,110
I'd look good even in a sack.

88
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:19,310
If you don't want a stepfather,

89
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,760
figure it out yourself.

90
00:10:25,130 --> 00:10:26,680
And this little rabbit...

91
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,930
Say thank you to the mister.

92
00:10:32,570 --> 00:10:33,650
Thank you, sir.

93
00:10:33,650 --> 00:10:34,650
Don't mention it.

94
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,480
He's a martial artist.

95
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,610
That's impressive.

96
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:38,750
Yes.

97
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,270
Not bad.

98
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:41,740
He's trained in the martial arts.

99
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,550
Impressive.

100
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,990
He's got some martial arts skills.

101
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:48,510
His skills are really awesome.

102
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:52,700
Mentor,

103
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,820
after becoming one of the Zhangs,

104
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:56,140
my body has grown more agile—

105
00:10:56,140 --> 00:10:57,740
I've truly become stronger.

106
00:10:58,370 --> 00:10:59,790
If you don't train,

107
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:02,990
having Zhang blood alone
will get you nowhere.

108
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:08,360
But I think you're really getting senile.

109
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,130
How could you

110
00:11:11,290 --> 00:11:13,420
let Zhang Haixia go on a mission alone?

111
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:15,700
His current physical condition

112
00:11:15,700 --> 00:11:16,720
can't handle it.

113
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:20,050
Only he knows the best
whether he can handle it or not.

114
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:22,620
He needs to be treated
as a normal person now.

115
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:23,630
Neither you nor I

116
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:26,250
have the right to make decisions for him.

117
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:29,050
But he's just recovered
from a serious condition.

118
00:11:32,850 --> 00:11:34,330
Stop messing around!

119
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:36,510
What are you trying to say?

120
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,300
He has really been

121
00:11:40,830 --> 00:11:41,690
acting weird lately.

122
00:11:41,690 --> 00:11:43,390
I feel like he's hiding something from me.

123
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:45,120
Did he take the wrong medicine?

124
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,260
Does that medicine

125
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:48,120
have any side effects?

126
00:11:48,370 --> 00:11:49,290
Maybe.

127
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:51,050
Since you're worried about him,

128
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:52,580
just keep a close eye on him.

129
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:55,050
What do you mean "maybe"?
Y-You have no idea?

130
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:57,740
Zhang Hailou, you've grown up a bit.

131
00:11:58,390 --> 00:12:00,390
It's time for you to take care of him.

132
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,750
Hurry up and look through the files.

133
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:16,320
[Investigation Report]

134
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:16,000
Zhang Qishan.

135
00:12:16,350 --> 00:12:17,720
[Zhang Qishan is from the Zhang family
in Northeast China]

136
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:18,940
[He's the grandson
of the former Zhang Qiling.]

137
00:12:19,170 --> 00:12:21,810
The Mo faction warlords once
committed crimes at Panhua Reef.

138
00:12:21,810 --> 00:12:23,610
Haixia's report stated that

139
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:27,040
the Mo faction warlords were
highly wary of one person.

140
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:28,250
That was Zhang Qishan.

141
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:30,550
From Panhua Reef all the way here...

142
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,130
Based on my assessment,

143
00:12:32,130 --> 00:12:34,340
ordinary people can't possibly
have swum this distance—

144
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:35,550
except for Zhang Qishan.

145
00:12:35,430 --> 00:12:36,180
[The foundation of the Old Nine Clans:
In Changxiang,]

146
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:37,520
Zhang Qishan is no ordinary man.

147
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:36,930
[Zhang Qishan gradually befriended
capable figures to build up his strength]

148
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:37,840
[and has successfully established
the Old Nine Clans now.]

149
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,580
He is the Defense Commander of Changxiang

150
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,700
[Zhang Qishan has used this case
to enhance his reputation]

151
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,410
[and his influence in Changxiang.]

152
00:12:39,580 --> 00:12:42,320
as well as the head
of the famous Old Nine Clans.

153
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:43,820
Old Nine Clans?

154
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,410
Are they famous?

155
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:46,580
I've never heard of them.

156
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:48,050
You spent most of your time in Nanyang.

157
00:12:48,050 --> 00:12:49,390
It's normal
that you haven't heard of them.

158
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:52,670
The Old Nine Clans are
9 prominent families in Changxiang.

159
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,620
They mainly deal
in tomb raiding and antiques.

160
00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:56,250
Their specific backgrounds are
very complicated.

161
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,340
Rumor has it
that these 9 families are omnipotent,

162
00:12:58,340 --> 00:13:00,960
and Zhang Qishan, their head,
is even more extraordinary.

163
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:04,080
He's nothing but a man with a military
and political background,

164
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,790
some dirty money from the business world,

165
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:06,770
and some power.

166
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,780
You're underestimating him.

167
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,700
Zhang Qishan

168
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:13,030
came from a declining family in the north.

169
00:13:13,050 --> 00:13:14,320
Despite his humble origins,

170
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,580
within just two years,

171
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,320
he has gained a foothold in Changxiang.

172
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,500
It's said that when he first arrived
in Changxiang,

173
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,760
he went on an outing with someone one day.

174
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:25,530
Seeing a giant Buddha statue
standing in the mountains,

175
00:13:25,530 --> 00:13:26,750
he made a bet

176
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:29,940
that he could bring
the giant Buddha statue home.

177
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,870
But the giant Buddha statue was built
against the mountain,

178
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,670
as tall as a bell tower.

179
00:13:34,050 --> 00:13:35,500
People simply didn't believe it.

180
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,600
But the next day,

181
00:13:38,010 --> 00:13:40,120
this giant Buddha statue really appeared

182
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,840
in the courtyard of his mansion.

183
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,220
The news spread

184
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:45,310
throughout the city overnight,

185
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:48,460
saying that Zhang Qishan knew
a mysterious transport technique—

186
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:49,920
the Five Ghosts Delivery.

187
00:13:50,290 --> 00:13:53,250
That's how Zhang Qishan
shot to fame overnight.

188
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:55,110
People all respectfully call him

189
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:56,820
Great Master Buddha Zhang.

190
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:58,280
Is he really that capable?

191
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:04,280
Have you fought him before?

192
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,880
We've had some contact.

193
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,460
But the problem is

194
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:11,290
that he doesn't want to see me.

195
00:14:11,370 --> 00:14:11,910
Why?

196
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:15,410
I read the Case Closure Report
of Panhua Reef back then

197
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:18,340
and saw that the warlords there were
so afraid of him.

198
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,770
It meant he was their enemy,

199
00:14:21,170 --> 00:14:23,770
or at least he had crossed paths
with Mo Yungao.

200
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:25,750
Later, I investigated Zhang Qishan

201
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:28,940
and directly sent some pros to Changxiang
for intelligence collection.

202
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:31,390
But he had eyes and ears
everywhere in Changxiang.

203
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:34,010
He actually caught the agents I sent

204
00:14:34,010 --> 00:14:34,960
within a day

205
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,560
and sent them out of the city.

206
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:37,960
Upon learning this,

207
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:40,360
I immediately mailed a gift from Xiacheng
to apologize,

208
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:42,500
hoping to use it as an excuse
to visit him.

209
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:44,030
But the next day,

210
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:45,890
the gift was returned

211
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,770
with an extra package from Changxiang.

212
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,790
"Not a third time"?

213
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:55,550
Zhang Qishan is quite arrogant.

214
00:14:55,890 --> 00:14:56,440
No.

215
00:14:57,790 --> 00:15:00,050
Actually, what he said reminded me.

216
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:01,320
A long time ago,

217
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,320
I heard a saying in the Zhang family.

218
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:05,360
"Having been separated by mountains
and seas for a thousand years,

219
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,020
we cannot reunite in sorrow."

220
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:10,890
In the Zhang family's proverb,
mountains and seas are

221
00:15:10,890 --> 00:15:13,230
two groups of people who can never meet.

222
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,920
When mountains and seas meet,

223
00:15:15,630 --> 00:15:17,410
the Zhang family is bound to perish.

224
00:15:17,410 --> 00:15:19,030
So when he told you
not to try a third time,

225
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,160
he was reminding you

226
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:23,630
that mountains and seas should never meet.

227
00:15:23,630 --> 00:15:25,080
But our trip this time

228
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:27,010
will be the third try.

229
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:33,920
By the way,

230
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,280
when I went down to the Archives before,

231
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,250
a weirdo changed his face

232
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:40,030
and followed me down.

233
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:41,250
I thought you sent him

234
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:42,630
to supervise me.

235
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:44,950
Now I'm wondering if it could be...

236
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,170
That's why I said

237
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,300
our trip to visit our relatives
in Changxiang this time

238
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:54,390
would definitely be full of obstacles.

239
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:55,320
If that's the case,

240
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,510
this family visit

241
00:15:57,460 --> 00:15:58,990
will be quite interesting.

242
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:21,820
[Changxiang City]

243
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:25,780
[Changxiang]

244
00:16:35,170 --> 00:16:37,100
Let's have something to eat first.

245
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:38,870
Sir,

246
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:40,700
2 bowls of rice noodles
and a pot of wine.

247
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:41,630
Coming right up.

248
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,620
Here you go.

249
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,370
These rice noodles

250
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:00,410
need some chili

251
00:17:00,410 --> 00:17:01,130
to taste better.

252
00:17:01,130 --> 00:17:02,410
It's mildly spicy. Give it a try.

253
00:17:02,410 --> 00:17:03,440
Mildly spicy?

254
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,770
Mildly spicy isn't enough.

255
00:17:04,770 --> 00:17:05,920
We need extra spicy.

256
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:07,260
Sir and madam,

257
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,920
I can tell you're not locals here
in Changxiang.

258
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,650
Mildly spicy is enough for you.

259
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:13,200
Hand me that chili.

260
00:17:13,770 --> 00:17:15,010
I think you guys in Changxiang

261
00:17:15,010 --> 00:17:16,960
really don't know how much chili
people who eat spicy food want.

262
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:17,980
Let me, someone from Xiacheng,

263
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,510
teach you, a local in Changxiang,
how to eat spicy food.

264
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:20,310
Bring it here.

265
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:21,540
Okay.

266
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,579
Here comes the chili.

267
00:17:35,010 --> 00:17:37,030
Here is the wine. Enjoy your meal.

268
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,280
I feel like no one is watching us.

269
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:43,700
Mentor, were we a bit

270
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:45,020
overreacting before?

271
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,430
Come and take a look at the magic trick!

272
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:54,500
Everyone, come and take a look.

273
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,460
Look over here!

274
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:01,510
Sir,

275
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:02,850
I'm terribly sorry.

276
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:03,590
So sorry.

277
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,180
Bro,

278
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:06,200
your magic trick

279
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:06,980
is so interesting.

280
00:18:06,980 --> 00:18:08,330
Why don't you conjure up
another bowl of noodles

281
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:09,330
to compensate me?

282
00:18:09,550 --> 00:18:10,400
Wait, this...

283
00:18:14,290 --> 00:18:14,960
Oh, lady,

284
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,850
judging by your looks and dress,

285
00:18:17,850 --> 00:18:19,650
you're not a local here, are you?

286
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:21,320
What are you talking about?

287
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:22,700
Well,

288
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:24,720
I see this lady

289
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:26,800
with a face full of depression.

290
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:28,940
There must be something troubling her.

291
00:18:28,940 --> 00:18:31,800
What makes you think
her face is full of depression?

292
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:33,840
Are you trying to hit on her?

293
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,910
I wouldn't dare, I wouldn't.

294
00:18:36,250 --> 00:18:38,380
I'm just a street performer.

295
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,660
I can do a bit of magic tricks,

296
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,190
I'm good at reading people,

297
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:42,850
and I can foresee the future.

298
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:44,070
Lady,

299
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:45,900
if you don't mind,

300
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:47,750
you can listen to my rambling for a bit.

301
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:48,500
Perhaps

302
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,350
it can ease your worries

303
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:51,550
and make you smile.

304
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:53,410
Nonsense. Swindler, step aside.

305
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,460
Sir, I want another bowl of rice noodles.

306
00:18:55,460 --> 00:18:56,390
Coming right up.

307
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,880
How is it nonsense?

308
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:01,020
Look at this lady's face.

309
00:19:01,850 --> 00:19:03,700
She is definitely no ordinary person.

310
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:05,050
Her forehead is full,

311
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:07,690
and her cheekbones are elegant and bright.

312
00:19:07,810 --> 00:19:09,940
Amazing.

313
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,420
Unlike this young man,

314
00:19:12,770 --> 00:19:14,850
who looks like he's been trapped
in a foreign land for a long time,

315
00:19:14,850 --> 00:19:16,770
hasn't seen much of the wider world,

316
00:19:16,770 --> 00:19:18,290
and is short-sighted

317
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:19,700
with no real ambition.

318
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:20,640
Yet he's...

319
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:22,700
-What are you saying?
-How much is it?

320
00:19:26,330 --> 00:19:27,130
Let go, let go.

321
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,330
Let go!

322
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:32,150
[Changxiang Rice Noodles]

323
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:29,830
Come on.

324
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:31,330
Miss.

325
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:32,420
Put it here.

326
00:19:32,420 --> 00:19:33,550
It's not expensive.

327
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,330
Six wen.

328
00:19:34,810 --> 00:19:35,610
Six wen?

329
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:37,530
I don't have 6 wen.

330
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:40,070
Keep the change.

331
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:47,140
Wow,

332
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:48,600
you're so generous, miss.

333
00:19:50,570 --> 00:19:53,100
Miss, I guess you came
to Changxiang this time

334
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,350
to look for an old acquaintance.

335
00:19:58,110 --> 00:19:59,680
What a pity.

336
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:02,240
"Searching high and low,

337
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,640
you cannot find them

338
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:06,090
anywhere."

339
00:20:08,110 --> 00:20:10,370
Your meeting with your old acquaintance

340
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:12,020
probably won't go smoothly.

341
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:14,130
And you will face many obstacles.

342
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,520
In addition to those obstacles,

343
00:20:16,610 --> 00:20:19,050
even if you see the person
you want to see,

344
00:20:19,050 --> 00:20:20,050
things

345
00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:22,440
may not go as you wish.

346
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:25,240
I'm afraid

347
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:28,020
there will even be a bloody disaster.

348
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:29,660
I hope you

349
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:31,720
can let go of your obsession.

350
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:32,440
Perhaps

351
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:34,340
you can escape a calamity.

352
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,830
Thank you for the reminder, sir.

353
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,940
But now I have no other choice.

354
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:41,990
I must see

355
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:44,080
my old acquaintance this time,

356
00:20:44,460 --> 00:20:46,190
no matter the cost.

357
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,380
I hope my old acquaintance

358
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,170
can understand my determination.

359
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:57,570
Seems like you've made up your mind, miss.

360
00:20:57,570 --> 00:20:58,200
And I am

361
00:20:58,770 --> 00:21:00,420
no more than a street performer.

362
00:21:00,420 --> 00:21:02,250
I can't force anything upon you.

363
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:06,030
Since the 6 wen

364
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:08,180
couldn't ease your worries,

365
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:09,310
how about

366
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,010
we consider

367
00:21:12,420 --> 00:21:14,330
this money on credit?

368
00:21:15,250 --> 00:21:16,050
In the future,

369
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:18,530
if you have anything to ask,

370
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:21,380
I'll give you an answer for free.

371
00:21:22,050 --> 00:21:22,650
Farewell.

372
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:26,420
Bro,

373
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:29,070
I think you're quite good at this.

374
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:31,800
Why don't you do
the fortune-telling for me, too?

375
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,700
I...

376
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:36,030
You can do magic tricks?

377
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:38,100
What a coincidence. So can I!

378
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:39,280
How about this?

379
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:40,350
I'll show you

380
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:41,270
a sword trick.

381
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:42,950
If the people here

382
00:21:42,970 --> 00:21:44,220
think it's good and tip me,

383
00:21:44,220 --> 00:21:45,240
I'll give the money to you.

384
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,200
If it's not good,

385
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,700
you won't lose anything either.

386
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:48,160
Wait...

387
00:21:49,850 --> 00:21:51,030
Who sent you?

388
00:21:53,030 --> 00:21:54,580
I'm just a fortune-teller.

389
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,840
Let me play with you a bit more.

390
00:21:58,940 --> 00:21:59,570
Bravo!

391
00:22:09,220 --> 00:22:10,440
Bravo!

392
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:11,810
Bravo!

393
00:22:11,810 --> 00:22:12,530
Bravo!

394
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:13,220
Bravo!

395
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:13,960
Amazing!

396
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,050
Nice!

397
00:22:32,910 --> 00:22:34,050
A murder!

398
00:22:34,050 --> 00:22:35,050
Run!

399
00:22:35,850 --> 00:22:36,980
Someone was killed!

400
00:22:37,570 --> 00:22:38,630
There's a murder!

401
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,250
Run!

402
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:42,290
He was killed!

403
00:23:13,060 --> 00:23:16,260
[Zhang Changlin,
Zhang Qishan's Lieutenant]

404
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:31,400
You desperado,

405
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,070
how dare you kill people in the streets?

406
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:35,130
[Changxiang Rice Noodles]

407
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:35,150
The audacity.

408
00:23:36,530 --> 00:23:37,950
It's you.

409
00:23:38,570 --> 00:23:40,900
So you work for Zhang Qishan.

410
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:46,230
You know him?

411
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:47,460
I do.

412
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:48,920
Remember I told you

413
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,240
about a guy who disguised himself
as my friend

414
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,420
and went down to the Archives with me?

415
00:23:51,420 --> 00:23:52,020
It was him.

416
00:23:56,660 --> 00:23:58,180
He's got a long reach,

417
00:23:58,180 --> 00:23:59,680
even extending into my territory.

418
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:01,610
There must be something wrong
with Zhang Qishan, our relative.

419
00:24:01,610 --> 00:24:03,090
We can't let this continue.

420
00:24:03,090 --> 00:24:04,880
-When I see him...
-Let's talk about it later.

421
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,610
-How can we talk about it later?
-We need his help.

422
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:09,910
What did you make such noise?

423
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,920
I was just praising you to my mentor.

424
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,220
Impressive.

425
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:15,240
You guys in Changxiang are so efficient.

426
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,240
You showed up

427
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:17,730
right after the incident.

428
00:24:17,810 --> 00:24:19,250
You were prepared in advance, huh?

429
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:21,610
Now we have both witnesses and evidence.

430
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:24,060
Are you still going to resist?

431
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:26,440
Then don't blame me for showing no mercy.

432
00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:49,500
What did you do?

433
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:53,330
I've been practicing brick breaking.

434
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:55,230
Tell me.

435
00:24:56,010 --> 00:24:56,920
Just now...

436
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:07,980
I...

437
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:08,750
Fire!

438
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,430
Why did you stop me?

439
00:25:22,510 --> 00:25:23,640
If you kill Zhang Qishan's men,

440
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,100
how can we ask him for help?

441
00:25:25,250 --> 00:25:27,710
How do you know
they will definitely help us?

442
00:25:28,460 --> 00:25:29,480
You killed him.

443
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:30,290
Go prove your innocence.

444
00:25:30,290 --> 00:25:30,760
What?

445
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:01,030
Zhang Hailou,

446
00:26:01,030 --> 00:26:03,030
someone asked me to show you the way.

447
00:26:03,150 --> 00:26:04,470
Come on, follow me.

448
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:20,960
Wait here and count to 100.

449
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,410
Don't come out until you count to 100.

450
00:26:22,410 --> 00:26:24,940
Then cross the street opposite
and turn left.

451
00:26:26,540 --> 00:26:27,980
How do you know my name?

452
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:35,240
Hurry! Find him!

453
00:26:36,290 --> 00:26:41,310
One, two, three, four, five.

454
00:26:59,220 --> 00:26:59,840
Search!

455
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:36,900
[Fengxing Photo Studio]

456
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,270
That was so scary.

457
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:40,090
Zhang Qishan told me

458
00:27:40,090 --> 00:27:41,350
not to try a third time.

459
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:44,290
So going to Changxiang
to find him this time

460
00:27:44,290 --> 00:27:45,810
will definitely be full of obstacles.

461
00:27:45,810 --> 00:27:47,210
Once I set foot in Changxiang,

462
00:27:47,210 --> 00:27:48,410
he will surely notice

463
00:27:48,530 --> 00:27:51,060
and try every means
to drive us out of the city.

464
00:27:51,610 --> 00:27:52,550
In this case,

465
00:27:53,290 --> 00:27:54,550
we might as well use it.

466
00:27:55,420 --> 00:27:56,830
You want to use yourself as bait

467
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:57,960
to test Zhang Qishan's attitude

468
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,960
toward us and the methods he'll use.

469
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:01,990
Zhang Hailou is

470
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:03,890
a great choice for drawing fire.

471
00:28:04,660 --> 00:28:06,520
So he and I will set off in the open,

472
00:28:07,380 --> 00:28:08,510
and you will move covertly

473
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:09,420
and flexibly.

474
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:13,920
Zhang Qishan is really cruel.

475
00:28:14,660 --> 00:28:16,440
Technically, I'm his uncle.

476
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:17,990
No, he's my cousin.

477
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:20,400
How could he try to kill me ruthlessly?

478
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,730
I don't think it's that simple.

479
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:25,180
Firstly, he has no reason to kill us.

480
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:26,570
Even if he wanted to kill us,

481
00:28:26,570 --> 00:28:28,160
there should be easier ways.

482
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:31,000
Why would he go to so much trouble
and frame you for murder?

483
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,000
What was that for?

484
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:33,000
To win a battle,

485
00:28:33,290 --> 00:28:34,790
speed prevails.

486
00:28:36,220 --> 00:28:37,480
On Zhang Qishan's turf,

487
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,810
as long as we move fast enough,

488
00:28:38,810 --> 00:28:40,380
even his chain of schemes

489
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,940
won't work.

490
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:44,770
Then let's split up.

491
00:28:48,850 --> 00:28:50,510
How are your legs recovering?

492
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:52,030
Look.

493
00:28:58,090 --> 00:28:58,690
Shrimpie.

494
00:29:12,420 --> 00:29:14,950
I finally don't have to push
your wheelchair.

495
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,320
Actually, my legs

496
00:29:23,570 --> 00:29:25,080
aren't fully healed.

497
00:29:25,740 --> 00:29:27,240
Fine, I can push it for you.

498
00:29:28,010 --> 00:29:29,530
Do you see that pillar ahead?

499
00:29:29,530 --> 00:29:31,160
We are at the same starting line.

500
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,600
If you can run faster than me,

501
00:29:32,600 --> 00:29:34,460
I'll push it one more time for you.

502
00:29:34,940 --> 00:29:36,260
Three, two, one. Go.

503
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,590
See? You gave up.

504
00:29:44,510 --> 00:29:46,420
Alright, let's get down to business.

505
00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:48,640
I think we should still stick together
and move.

506
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,420
Any ideas?

507
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,880
About the street performer you met,

508
00:29:54,180 --> 00:29:55,480
was he a decent-looking scholar,

509
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,700
wearing glasses,

510
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:58,360
talking in a mysterious tone,

511
00:29:58,750 --> 00:30:00,530
looking very much like a fortune-teller?

512
00:30:00,530 --> 00:30:02,790
When exactly did you come to Changxiang?

513
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:07,700
That person is no street performer,

514
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,670
but from the Eighth Clan
of the Nine Clans.

515
00:30:09,670 --> 00:30:13,130
He's Qi Tiezui, the Eighth Master Qi,
known as the Divine Seer.

516
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:16,290
A member of the Nine Clans?

517
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,790
This Qi family is

518
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:20,750
pretty special among the Nine Clans.

519
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:22,220
Other forces rely on opening stores

520
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:23,420
to build their power.

521
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,850
But Qi Tiezui

522
00:30:25,230 --> 00:30:26,430
only needs one store,

523
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:28,610
and it's a fortune-telling shop.

524
00:30:28,430 --> 00:30:30,790
[Buy One & Get
One Fortune-Telling for Free]

525
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:30,000
Take care, sir.

526
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:31,460
Sir, want to tell your fortune?

527
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,150
Normally speaking...

528
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:32,750
Come in, please.

529
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,750
Such a small shop

530
00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:36,050
would have easily been eliminated
in Changxiang.

531
00:30:36,050 --> 00:30:37,160
But the Qi family

532
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,890
has survived for generations,

533
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,460
and their business
has always been booming.

534
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,610
It's because Qi Tiezui

535
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,950
has a very weird habit.

536
00:30:46,270 --> 00:30:47,700
As long as a customer buys something,

537
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:49,030
he tells their fortune.

538
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:51,260
It's called a free fortune-telling.

539
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:52,740
And he's incredibly accurate.

540
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:53,880
Thank you.

541
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:55,200
The Eighth Mystic Seer,

542
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,250
known as the best fortune-teller
in Changxiang,

543
00:30:57,250 --> 00:30:58,850
has no equal in Changxiang.

544
00:31:00,490 --> 00:31:02,310
The Archives investigated him, too.

545
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,710
The evaluation of him is,

546
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:06,180
"miraculous."

547
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:08,500
He relies on his ability
to see through the world's secrets.

548
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:10,900
Great Master Buddha Zhang
highly values him

549
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:13,360
and even takes him along
when solving cases.

550
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:18,110
Since Zhang Qishan is
on such good terms with him,

551
00:31:19,610 --> 00:31:21,740
he probably wouldn't bear to kill him.

552
00:31:24,010 --> 00:31:26,250
If I were Great Master Buddha Zhang,

553
00:31:26,550 --> 00:31:28,810
I would have definitely hidden him well.

554
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:34,130
What scheme are you cooking up again?

555
00:31:34,290 --> 00:31:36,050
You can run, but you can't hide.

556
00:31:39,280 --> 00:31:43,820
[Qi Tiezui, from the Eighth Clan
of the Old Nine Clans]

557
00:31:44,050 --> 00:31:45,740
Changxiang City

558
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:48,310
is not peaceful today.

559
00:31:50,630 --> 00:31:51,250
Fire!

560
00:31:51,250 --> 00:31:52,140
It's on fire!

561
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:52,680
Fire!

562
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:53,740
It's on fire!

563
00:31:53,740 --> 00:31:54,550
Come put out the fire! Hurry!

564
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:55,530
Put out the fire!

565
00:31:55,530 --> 00:31:56,510
Put it out!

566
00:31:59,330 --> 00:32:00,260
Put out the fire!

567
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:04,200
It looks like this fire

568
00:32:04,770 --> 00:32:06,480
will burn for a while.

569
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,140
Oh, no!

570
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:13,640
Well...

571
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:16,240
Isn't this the location of my house?

572
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,060
Eighth Master,

573
00:32:18,330 --> 00:32:19,350
Great Master Buddha instructed

574
00:32:19,350 --> 00:32:20,380
that you cannot go out.

575
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:22,000
My house is on fire!

576
00:32:23,030 --> 00:32:23,900
You know what?

577
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:25,880
Our Qi family's ancient scrolls
and secret texts spanning 7 generations

578
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:26,940
are all inside there!

579
00:32:26,940 --> 00:32:27,940
If they burn down,

580
00:32:28,110 --> 00:32:30,000
your Great Master Buddha
can't afford the compensation even if he

581
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:30,920
sells the Zhang's Residence!

582
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,770
Get out of the way!

583
00:32:31,770 --> 00:32:32,430
Move aside!

584
00:32:33,250 --> 00:32:34,110
Eighth Master!

585
00:32:34,940 --> 00:32:36,200
Isn't this the fortune-teller's house?

586
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:36,980
Why is it on fire?

587
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:37,940
This is too scary.

588
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:38,550
Exactly.

589
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:39,410
So terrifying.

590
00:32:40,990 --> 00:32:42,020
My blanket!

591
00:32:44,930 --> 00:32:45,380
You...

592
00:32:45,380 --> 00:32:46,420
My blanket!

593
00:33:12,210 --> 00:33:13,110
Street performer,

594
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,400
I see your head is

595
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:16,000
still on your neck, huh?

596
00:33:17,290 --> 00:33:18,230
Bro,

597
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,680
it looks like you will

598
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,480
lose your head today.

599
00:33:27,770 --> 00:33:30,050
How dare you two little rogues

600
00:33:30,050 --> 00:33:31,630
act wildly here?

601
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:34,680
Do you know what kind of place
Changxiang is?

602
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:37,140
I don't think you can
escape anywhere today.

603
00:33:38,110 --> 00:33:39,910
Who said we were going to escape?

604
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:41,360
Eighth Master,

605
00:33:41,850 --> 00:33:42,980
are you still alive?

606
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:45,290
I'm still alive!

607
00:33:45,890 --> 00:33:47,620
Whether he will be alive or dead

608
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:50,330
depends on my mood.

609
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,050
How about this?

610
00:33:52,050 --> 00:33:53,310
Firstly, apologize to me

611
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,030
sincerely.

612
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:56,460
And then bring Zhang Qishan here.

613
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:58,040
I will only talk to him.

614
00:34:00,350 --> 00:34:02,200
You committed arson, caused trouble,

615
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:04,050
and kidnapped innocent civilians.

616
00:34:04,050 --> 00:34:05,550
With multiple crimes combined,

617
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,850
you will be severely punished.

618
00:34:06,850 --> 00:34:08,260
Release him immediately,

619
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:10,219
or we'll shoot you to death.

620
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:10,900
I...

621
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:12,500
I'm still inside!

622
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:14,100
Don't you care about my life?

623
00:34:14,780 --> 00:34:15,639
Eighth Master,

624
00:34:16,170 --> 00:34:17,980
why didn't you wait for me here
before going in?

625
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:18,989
What nonsense!

626
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:20,370
If my house burns down,

627
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:22,510
can you take responsibility for that?

628
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,320
Go.

629
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:38,310
Seven.

630
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:19,250
My enamel pearl patterned vase...

631
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,320
Of all the things

632
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,480
you could throw,

633
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:24,270
why did you throw this one?
